|Example.English translation="He stressed that in Mexico there are problems, but higher education is one of the levers that can help minimize them."
|Example.Provenance=http://www.cronica.com.mx/notas/2010/493903.html
|Example.Comments="ayudar a amortiguarlos"

forces here- social problems are forces (physical) and higher education is a force(barrier) that can diminish the force of the social problems as it(social problem force) impacts Mexico
